			"system":{
				"description":{
					"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>The ghostly shape of an enormous part of the ceiling crashes down, leaving the actual ceiling intact. When it strikes the floor, it explodes in a cascade of light.</i></p><p><b>Trap</b></p>",
