		{
			"name":"Countermeasures",
			"type":"feature",
			"img":"icons/svg/cancel.svg",
			"system":{
				"description":{
					"value":"<ul><li><b>Arcana DC 24:</b> After the trap triggers, a successful Arcana check stops the trap from triggering in one of the indicated areas only.</li><li><b>Perception DC 24:</b> The character who uses a minor action and succeeds on the check can see where the cascade falls next.</li><li>* Dispel magic against Will 35 ends the trap's effect.</li></ul>",
